quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  22,38,"Pellet, Alla O solnanay(dunyanay) …ìen gom…óin…ìe, pellet, Alla O yi…óaa kala hodoowo heewu…óo geddi"
  22,39,"Du≈ãanaama …ìen wonaa…ìe ha…ìeede [yo…ìtagol] sabu kam…ìe ko …ìe too√±aa…ìe, pellet, Alla ko O Hattan…óo e dow wallugol …ìe"
  22,40,"∆Åen yaltinaa…ìe ka galleeji mu'un ko aldaa e goo- nga si wanaa fii tun …ìe wi'ii: \"Joomi amen ko Alla\". Sinndo wanaano Alla du√±irde yim…ìe …ìen yoga e ma…ì…ìe yoga, yirbinteno rewir…ói ruhbaaniyankoo…ìe …ìen e rewir…ói Annasaara en e rewir…ói Alyahuuda en e Juulir…óe …óe Innde Alla ja≈ãtetee e nder mu'un ko heewi. ma Alla wallu …ìen walloo…ìe Mo, pellet, Alla ko O Dolnu…óo Teddu…óo"
  22,41,∆Åen taw…ìe si Men newinanii …ìe ka leydi …ìe √±innay Julde nden …ìe totta askaal on …ìe yamira ko mo∆¥∆¥i kon …ìe ha…óa ko boni kon. Ko Alla woodani …ìattane fiyakuuji …óin
  22,42,"Si …ìe fennii ma, haray gom…óii fenniino ado ma…ì…ìe yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen e Aadinkoo…ìe …ìen e Samuudinkoo…ìe …ìen"
  22,43,E yim…ìe Ibraahiima …ìen e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen
  22,44,"E yim…ìe Madyana …ìen Muusaa kadi fennaama, Mi nennani yeddu…ìe …ìen refti Mi nanngi …ìe, ko honno yagginngol Am ngol wonirnoo"
  22,45,"No foti hewde e Saare nde Men halki …óum tawi ko nde too√±unde, hara hinde ajjii e hoore kippudiiji mayre, e woyndu yirbundu e hu…ìeere toowunde [eggaande]"
  22,46,"Enee, hara …ìee yahaali ka leydi sakko laatanoo…ìe …ìer…óe …ìe haqqilira …óe, maa…óum noppi …ìe nanira …ói? Pellet, [ko woni kon] wanaa gite …óen wumi, kono ko …ìer…óe wonu…óe …óen e nder becce …óen wumi"
  22,47,"Hi…ìe …óa…ì…ìire yaccinaneede Lepte …óen, [e …óum le] Alla lunndataako fodoore Makko nden. Pellet √±allal ka Joomi maa…óa ko wano duu…ìi wuluure no limorton non"
  22,48,"No foti heewde e saare nde Mi nennani …óum hara kayre ko nde too√±unde, refti Mi nannginde ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde nden"
  22,49,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe, anndee min ko mi jertinoowo on …ìanngu…óo"
  22,50,∆Åen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin no woodani …ìe haforanal e arsike teddu…óo
  22,51,"∆Åen yaccii…ìe [fii bonnugol] e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe ronkinaa [Men] ko …ìen …óon woni yim…ìe Jahiimaawe ngen"
  22,52,"Men Nulaali ado maa…óa immorde e Nulaa…óo wanaa kadi Annabaajo si wanaa si o janngii Seytaane werloto e nder janki makko kin. Alla itta ko Seytaane werlii kon, refti Alla tabintina Aayeeje Makko …óen. Alla ko O Anndu…óo √ëee√±u…óo"
  22,53,"Fii yo O wa…óu ko Seytaane werlotoo ko njarraboye wonannde …ìen …ìe nawnaare woni ka …ìer…óe mu'un e …ìe …ìer…óe mu'un yoori …ìen. Pellet, too√±oo…ìe …ìen …ìe wonii e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  22,54,"Fii yo …ìen okkaa…ìe Ganndal ngal anndu pellet, ko [Alqur'aanaare nden woni] Goonga kan immorde ka Joomi maa…óa …ìe gom…óina nde, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yankinanoo …óum. Pellet Alla Fewnay …ìen gom…óin…ìe faade e Laawol Focciingol"
  22,55,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe seerataa hi…ìe e nder sikke [fii Alqur'aana] haa Darngal ngal ara e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee maa…óum ara e ma…ì…ìe Lepte √ëalaande sa…ótunde"
  22,56,"Laamu ngun nden √ëalnde ko Alla heeranii O √ëaawoyay hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, …ìen gom…óin…ìe …ìe golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i …óin hi…ìe e nder Aljannaaji Neemii…ói"
  22,57,"∆Åen yeddu…ìe, …ìe fenni kadi Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìen …óon no woodani …ìe lepte hoynooje"
  22,58,"∆Åen feru…ìe e Laawol Alla refti …ìe waraa maa…óum …ìe maayi Alla arsikoyay …ìe arsike mo∆¥∆¥o. Pellet, Alla ko Kanko woni …ìuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Arsikoo…ìe"
  22,59,"Ma O naadoy…ìe naatirgal ngal …ìe welaa …óum. Pellet, Alla ko O Anndu…óo Mu√±√±ii…óo"